headline: Take-Two Interactive CEO Strauss Zelnick spends 25% of his time on mentoring, and he starts with two simple challenges
summary: Take-Two Interactive CEO Strauss Zelnick has been mentoring and coaching people in business world for decades. He says the success recipe changes each time.
